The prices of diesel and paraffin are also set to increase by 63c/litre and up to 76c/litre respectively. JOHANNESBURG - The Department of Energy has announced that the price of petrol will increase by 45 cents a litre from 2 November.Diesel will rise by 63 cents a litre and illuminating paraffin by up to 76 cents per litre.More to follow on this developing story.